HEADWORD: Magnoliaceae
<hw>Magnoliaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A natural family of plants, a
subclass of the Magnoliidae; it includes the genera
<gen>Liriodendron</gen>; <gen>Magnolia</gen>; <gen>Manglietia</gen>; and
<gen>Michelia</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Magnoliaceae</fam>, magnolia
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
